# Karpathy Repositories Overview

Andrej Karpathy's GitHub hosts some of the most popular educational AI/ML repositories. Here's a comprehensive overview of his key projects.

## By Category

### LLM Training
- [[nanoGPT]] - Fastest GPT training (56.7k stars)
- [[llm-c]] - Pure C/CUDA training (29.5k stars)
- [[mingpt]] - Minimal PyTorch implementation (24.1k stars)

### Tokenization
- [[minbpe]] - Minimal BPE (10.4k stars)

### Neural Networks
- [[micrograd]] - Tiny autograd (15.4k stars)
- [[char-rnn]] - Character RNN (12k stars)

