## Common Patterns Across Repos

1. **Minimalism** - All repos prioritize readable, minimal code
2. **Educational** - Designed for learning, not production
3. **Self-contained** - Minimal dependencies

## Learning Path

1. Start with [[micrograd]] - Understand autograd
2. Learn [[minbpe]] - Understand tokenization
3. Study [[mingpt]] - Understand Transformer architecture
4. Use [[nanoGPT]] - Practical training
5. Optimize with [[llm-c]] - Performance

